{"tid":2478723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"營救理大案家長車司機被加控妨礙司法公正 保釋金大幅提升至十萬 需每日警署報到","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T10:46:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"18a2334da395e1f697b920a6879735b2cffb4661","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14840&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=19e569f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14840</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #轉介文件<br />\n👤梁(23) #1120紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月20日，在尖沙咀不遠處的暢通道南（地圖顯示現場為理工大學香港專上學院對開）涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛私家車。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：妨礙司法公正<br />\n(稍後補上)<br />\n===============<br />\n‼️控方表示有新增控罪，並申請撤銷被告擔保‼️<br />\n<br />\n✅法庭拒絕控方撤銷被告擔保的申請，唯被告需要遵守新修訂的保釋的條件✅<br />\n-保釋金提升至$100,000<br />\n-每天到警署報到<br />\n-其他條件依舊<br />\n<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年4月27日14:30在區域法院進行答辯程序，聆訊會用中文進行。<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示會保留不在場證據。"},{"pid":"cce1c6230cc570c7245caa0b594885920e8ca353","tid":2478723,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32b85ba73eacff595cfadfe007e97ce5131d3e7","tid":2478723,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"5b2c6dc7f8689876393b8721cf37afde28f2662c","tid":2478723,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb719b37b8a5ef729c1fa9e08b32518c0ac09c8","tid":2478723,"uid":74282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f7c39d417f812dca21ef6960779e245583c7b6","tid":2478723,"uid":157532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf41b99ad6a04a3f0929742c9b0ecc14e671d508","tid":2478723,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5295666d69a18901abf9c66a1f27bdab243b5c","tid":2478723,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b965acf1253c85e97ee7e8af9dcd87c9c8641511","tid":2478723,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"危駕老妨都想唔比人保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb632fa7dd3a313f63787c7960316d4ad6d2312","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #轉介文件<br />\n👤陳(32) #1118紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月18日，在紅磡繞道近理工大學李兆基樓涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛客貨車。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：妨礙司法公正<br />\n================<br />\n辯方表示不反對控罪的修訂，亦保留不在場證據。<br />\n<br />\n✅控方撤回撤銷擔保的申請✅<br />\n<br />\n法庭批准被告繼續保釋，唯需遵守更嚴格的保釋條件：<br />\n-保釋金需提升至$100,000<br />\n-每天到警署報到<br />\n-若地址更改需24小時前通知警署<br />\n-其他條件依舊<br />\n<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年4月27日14:30在區域法院進行答辯程序，聆訊會用中文進行。"},{"pid":"f58714fa23ebf33834c1b946f2296954fc8f619d","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"嚴官唔洗還押已經好好"},{"pid":"2142cc13e37af178a447efc2baad5a45a0ad4ed2","tid":2478723,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58714fa23ebf33834c1b946f2296954fc8f619d","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"嚴官唔洗還押已經好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"算係咁拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f295054dc14c94fa964387d2baa85f9515c55f3b","tid":2478723,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"好彩比保"},{"pid":"cf0d97ce3a23cd15061d708d60d4b8793733ff2c","tid":2478723,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2acd214b9c090b53b180ce42a05ec104e92525","tid":2478723,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f58714fa23ebf33834c1b946f2296954fc8f619d","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"嚴官唔洗還押已經好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"依個官一時時<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd073900592e9e0a7d04e62b8a22ee2d08aa896","tid":2478723,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"保到就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286a3f66963fb3c61f89e85b5cf0d8989508cc29","tid":2478723,"uid":93615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fe78af10cb390024b0cbf94a25e173e158e605","tid":2478723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"點撚樣妨礙司法公正呀又？"},{"pid":"07cb2b7293f5fb2d81b5a49c4447d3d379fd608c","tid":2478723,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f34c44b0fafcf3205298bf0a3f9f931a9df284","tid":2478723,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fe78af10cb390024b0cbf94a25e173e158e605","tid":2478723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"點撚樣妨礙司法公正呀又？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"呼吸都係妨礙司法公正"},{"pid":"a800e351a6ffd3266cc0fed925a2ba7f442e621e","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"據了解，案發時有車停泊在連接理工大學的一條水渠外，有人從渠底出來並登上汽車。警員嘗試截停查問時車子突然開動，撞到警員的大腿。此外，涉案時亦有汽車停泊在理大校舍外，接載從校舍游繩而下的人士。"},{"pid":"4cfd2f80b5efc042471326cb38278ea6b465b35a","tid":2478723,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"cls"}]}